{"tid":867743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外公切排骨時滑倒　1歲女童慘遭剁斷手掌","createTime":"2018-10-19T02:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-20T04:30:22.000Z","uid":130626,"like":159,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"f2fcf6a9da1c1ee3d3a8bcf572eb9d84e5ea351b","tid":867743,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:17:03.000Z","msg":"廚房是最容易發生居家意外的地方。中國甘肅省蘭州市一名1歲9個月大的女童，日前趁外公在廚房剁排骨的時候，跑到他身邊，沒想到女童腳滑了一下，外公的菜刀剛好落下，一刀斬斷了女童的手掌，家人即時將女童送醫搶救。<br />\n <br />\n事發在前日，這名外公姓張，他說，「我在切肉，外孫女跌倒了，正好刀落下去切到手了......手在上面，刀就下去了！」他見狀馬上抓住外孫女的傷口，開車將她送醫，而且一邊開車，一邊致電醫院求助。<br />\n <br />\n到醫院後，醫師檢查發現女童的左腕骨幾乎被斬斷，而且出現創傷失血性休克，醫護人員除要為她抗休克外，還緊急動手術，為女童接回斷肢。醫師稱，女童目前情況穩定，接回的斷肢血液輸送良好。<br />\n <br />\n「現在很多家長都不能看管好自己的小孩！」不少網友都批評當時照顧女童的外公粗心大意，同時，很多家長亦發現兒童很喜歡到廚房玩耍，一定要警誡：「我砍骨或者媳婦砍骨時，必定多次喊3歲的兒子不要靠近，危險危險的，必須喊！」（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181019/640_9addc5e1ebb52fcf4304d6d4c3e61860.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181019%2F640_9addc5e1ebb52fcf4304d6d4c3e61860.jpg&h=83899fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1歲女童在外公切排骨時跑進廚房，結果滑倒，被外公一刀斬斷手掌。翻攝《梨視頻》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181019/1450196/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181019%2F1450196%2F&d=XQV7Qy084sY5fMiQ%2BTOdzJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=15c43101\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181019%2F1450196%2F&h=b7e22107\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181019/1450196/</a>"},{"pid":"ef8d6f5c30e405a695f050066e052160c370febb","tid":867743,"uid":43041,"like":240,"dislike":3,"score":237,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"外公喺地下切肉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9e0a483bc7d7a2f968d1f5057ef30d6256b1ad9","tid":867743,"uid":92664,"like":460,"dislike":10,"score":450,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TpeV4wP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpeV4wP.jpg&h=51ebff3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bdf7f467f4c802fefc4a9d830ff9c33e91712c","tid":867743,"uid":2772,"like":52,"dislike":9,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:47:23.000Z","msg":"都係豬姐"},{"pid":"7f436af5fdc712d0594e651a41c2d2b3e3c35101","tid":867743,"uid":58147,"like":191,"dislike":2,"score":189,"quote":{"pid":"ef8d6f5c30e405a695f050066e052160c370febb","tid":867743,"uid":43041,"like":240,"dislike":3,"score":237,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:39:53.000Z","msg":"外公喺地下切肉？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:49:31.000Z","msg":"大陸嘛。<br />\n好多都mou喺地下切嘢，洗菜洗衫。"},{"pid":"c6b63328d9bb1cdd94f943eb646584566a37655a","tid":867743,"uid":4917,"like":3,"dislike":38,"score":-35,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:51:20.000Z","msg":"咩刀咁利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891ef0ced11dff9646aa8bfe2fbd0ca548409dd7","tid":867743,"uid":1550,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T02:54:03.000Z","msg":"個標題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e7b072a5c76aab9c08d6153655bf3823cdc790","tid":867743,"uid":126273,"like":300,"dislike":1,"score":299,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T03:08:59.000Z","msg":"究竟係邊個滑倒<br />\n<br />\n個女童滑倒點樣可以理解成咁既標題？"},{"pid":"893ffcbd27e4897b80cb10c14c07e03689dd1726","tid":867743,"uid":141871,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"c6b63328d9bb1cdd94f943eb646584566a37655a"